data.name: Label1.Text
data.value: Formula field uses a simple formatting system to evaluate the entry. The Following Basic Operations are valid. Formula can be used with static numbers also (ex. 1 + A.str) Addition = '+' Subtraction = '-' Multiplcation = '*' Division = '/'

data.name: Label2.Text
data.value: For stat variables, the format is: <Party's Letter ('A' or 'B')>.<start abbreviation> ex. 'A.str', 'A.dex, 'A.vit', 'A.int', 'A.mnd', 'A.pie', 'A.skb', 'A.roll' 'B.str', 'B.dex, 'B.vit', 'B.int', 'B.mnd', 'B.pie', 'B.skb', 'B.roll'
